comment: Ilyasova (ORL) makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) as he is backing up.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that possession be awarded to TOR was overturned and possession was awarded to ORL.

Oladipo (ORL) makes contact with Ross (TOR) that affects his RSBQ.
Powell (TOR) makes contact with Jennings's (ORL) body during his driving shot attempt.
Ilyasova (ORL) makes contact with DeRozan (TOR) that affects his RSBQ.
LATR and LHH show that Biyombo (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Fournier (ORL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
